tool_description: This API retrieves data of chemical elements and their properties collected from authoritative sources in JSON format
title: Chemical Elements

api_list.name: Get All Chemical Elements
api_list.description: This endpoint will return back data of all Chemical Elements of the periodic table
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://chemical-elements.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "chemical-elements.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
